        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials & Social Proof Section -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Don't Just Take Our Word For It
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            See why recovery facilities nationwide choose Sober Living App to transform their operations
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="flex mb-4">
              {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed italic">
              "Sober Living App transformed our operations. We've reduced administrative time by 60% and increased our occupancy rate by 35%. The ROI was evident within the first month."
